  }, "Practical Tips for Designing Test Cases"), mdx("p", null, "Writing good tests cases requires a lot of thought: you need to think about a wide variety of things that can go wrong. Here are some suggestions to guide your thinking, as well as important lessons. First, some thoughts for testing error cases:"), mdx("ul", null, mdx("li", {
